JUMPTOFIRSTMESSAGE_SETTINGS_ALIGNMENT_NO: The horizontal alignment of the button in the channels.
JUMPTOFIRSTMESSAGE_SETTINGS_FORUMS_ONLY_: Whether to display the button in forum posts only. It's recommended to leave this option enabled.
JUMPTOFIRSTMESSAGE_SETTINGS_JUMP_TO_UNRE: Will jump to the last unread message, if available, before jumping to the first message of the channel.
